Detailed Description

cvmx_pko_reg_queue_ptrs1

Notes: This CSR is used with PKO_MEM_QUEUE_PTRS and PKO_MEM_QUEUE_QOS to allow access to queues 128-255 and to allow up mapping of up to 16 queues per port. When programming queues 128-255, the programming sequence must first write PKO_REG_QUEUE_PTRS1 and then write PKO_MEM_QUEUE_PTRS or PKO_MEM_QUEUE_QOS for each queue. See the descriptions of PKO_MEM_QUEUE_PTRS and PKO_MEM_QUEUE_QOS for further explanation of queue programming.
